Ninja Warrior: UK - Series 4, Episode 5




Semi-Final 1

Competitors from across the UK test their strength, speed and courage in the semi-final of the obstacle-course challenge, hosted by Ben Shephard, Rochelle Humes and Chris Kamara. Those who make it to the end of the adrenaline-fuelled mission face one final task - scaling the heights of a tower named Mount Midoriyama - as they battle it out for a place in the grand final.




Original Air Date: 12-May-2018
